<!-- 定義及症狀 -->
'''砷中毒'''是一種肇因於體內[[砷|砷]]含量提升的醫學病徵<ref name="Va2007">{{Cite journal|title=Arsenic neurotoxicity — A review|url=http://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/0960327107084539|last=Vahidnia|first=A.|last2=van der Voet|first2=G.B.|date=2007-10|journal=Human & Experimental Toxicology|issue=10|doi=10.1177/0960327107084539|volume=26|pages=823–832|language=en|issn=0960-3271|pmid=18025055|last3=de Wolff|first3=F.A.|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411001614/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/0960327107084539|dead-url=no}}</ref>，指動物體內重要的代謝酵素，在砷的影響下受[[別構調節|別構調節]]作用而導致。一般也視為是[[有毒重金屬|重金屬]]中毒。若於短時間產生砷中毒現象，其症狀可能包含：[[頭痛|頭痛]]、[[暈眩|暈眩]]、[[嘔吐|嘔吐]]、[[腹痛|腹痛]]、{{le|腦病變|Encephalopathy}}以及帶[[血|血液]]的水狀[[腹瀉|腹瀉]]<ref name="Rat2003">{{Cite journal|title=Acute and chronic arsenic toxicity|url=https://pmj.bmj.com/lookup/doi/10.1136/pmj.79.933.391|last=Ratnaike|first=R N|date=2003-07-01|journal=Postgraduate Medical Journal|issue=933|doi=10.1136/pmj.79.933.391|volume=79|pages=391–396|language=en|issn=0032-5473|pmc=PMC1742758|pmid=12897217}}</ref>。長期接觸會導致皮膚增厚、[[足|足]]部[[角化症|角化症]]、{{le|黑色素沉澱|Hyperpigmentation}}、腹痛、腹瀉、[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]、[[周邊神經病變|周邊神經病變]]和[[癌症|癌症]]<ref name="Rat2003" />。

<!-- 病因及診斷 -->
長期接觸到砷的原因中，最常見於受污染的[[飲用水|飲用水]]<ref name=EH2013/>，[[地下水|地下水]]最常遭到污染的原因是來自大自然，[[採礦|採礦業]]和農耕也可能會污染地下水<ref name="Rat2003" />，土壤和空氣中也可能含有砷<ref name="Hug2011">{{Cite journal|title=Arsenic Exposure and Toxicology: A Historical Perspective|url=https://academic.oup.com/toxsci/article/1685876/Arsenic|last=Hughes|first=Michael F.|last2=Beck|first2=Barbara D.|date=2011-10|journal=Toxicological Sciences|issue=2|doi=10.1093/toxsci/kfr184|volume=123|pages=305–332|language=en|issn=1096-6080|pmc=PMC3179678|pmid=21750349|last3=Chen|first3=Yu|last4=Lewis|first4=Ari S.|last5=Thomas|first5=David J.|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112013855/https://academic.oup.com/toxsci/article/1685876/Arsenic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。建議水中的砷含量需小於為10-50µg/L（10-50 [[ppb|ppb]]）<ref name="Rat2003" />。其他的接觸方式為{{le|有害廢棄物|toxic waste sites}}、[[傳統醫藥|傳統醫藥]]<ref name="Rat2003" /><ref name=EH2013/>。多數的中毒病例為意外接觸所導致<ref name="Rat2003" />。砷的作用會影響約200 種[[酶|酶]]<ref name="Rat2003" />，確診方式為驗尿、驗血及檢驗頭髮<ref name="Rat2003" />。

<!-- 治療 -->
預防方式是避免使用高砷含量的水<ref name="Rat2003" />，可透過專用過濾器來過濾使用水，或使用雨水<ref name="Rat2003" />，關於長期砷中毒的治療，尚未有足夠證據能證實療效<ref name="Rat2003" />。針對急性砷中毒的處置方式，[[脱水|脱水]]的治療至關重要<ref name="Va2007" />。[[二巰基丁二酸|二巰基丁二酸]]（DMSA）或[[2,3-二巰基丙磺酸|2,3-二巰基丙磺酸]]（DMSP）可用來進行治療；但不建議使用[[二巰基丙醇|二巰基丙醇]]（BAL）<ref name="An2016">{{Cite journal|title=A review of pitfalls and progress in chelation treatment of metal poisonings|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0946672X16300311|last=Andersen|first=Ole|last2=Aaseth|first2=Jan|date=2016-12|journal=Journal of Trace Elements in Medicine and Biology|doi=10.1016/j.jtemb.2016.03.013|volume=38|pages=74–80|language=en|pmid=27150911|hdl=11250/2430866|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2019-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190505191720/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0946672X16300311|dead-url=no}}</ref>。砷中毒有可能要進行[[血液透析|血液透析]]<ref name="Va2007" />。

<!-- 歷史和文化 -->
全球超過兩億人因飲用水的污染，暴露在高於安全值的砷環境中<ref name=EH2013/>，而[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]和印度的[[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]則是危害最嚴重之區域<ref name=EH2013/>。在貧窮與弱勢群體中，暴露於高砷環境的狀況更為嚴重<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Systematic review of differential inorganic arsenic exposure in minority, low-income, and indigenous populations in the United States|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0160412016300113|last=Joca|first=Lauren|last2=Sacks|first2=Jason D.|date=2016-07|journal=Environment International|doi=10.1016/j.envint.2016.01.011|volume=92-93|pages=707–715|language=en|pmid=26896853|last3=Moore|first3=Danielle|last4=Lee|first4=Janice S.|last5=Sams|first5=Reeder|last6=Cowden|first6=John|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818030124/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0160412016300113|dead-url=no}}</ref>；急性的砷中毒反而不常見<ref name="EH2013">{{Cite journal|title=The Broad Scope of Health Effects from Chronic Arsenic Exposure: Update on a Worldwide Public Health Problem|url=https://ehp.niehs.nih.gov/doi/10.1289/ehp.1205875|last=Naujokas|first=Marisa F.|last2=Anderson|first2=Beth|date=2013-03|journal=Environmental Health Perspectives|issue=3|doi=10.1289/ehp.1205875|volume=121|pages=295–302|language=en|issn=0091-6765|pmc=PMC3621177|pmid=23458756|last3=Ahsan|first3=Habibul|last4=Aposhian|first4=H. Vasken|last5=Graziano|first5=Joseph H.|last6=Thompson|first6=Claudia|last7=Suk|first7=William A.|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322205246/https://ehp.niehs.nih.gov/doi/10.1289/ehp.1205875|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
關於砷毒性的醫學記載，可追溯至西元前16世紀{{le|埃伯斯氏古醫籍|Ebers papyrus}}<ref>{{Cite book|title=Care and Conservation of Geological Material|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kTz_AQAAQBAJ&pg=PA135|publisher=Routledge|date=2013-11-05|isbn=978-1-135-38521-7|language=en|first=Frank|last=Howie|page=135|access-date=2019-02-18|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612014701/https://books.google.com/books?id=kTz_AQAAQBAJ&pg=PA135|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在中国古典文学里面，砒霜（三氧化二砷）常常出现，如小说《[[水浒传|水浒传]]》里潘金莲毒杀武大郎的毒药就是砒霜。此外[[法兰西第一帝国|法兰西第一帝国]]皇帝[[拿破仑·波拿巴|拿破仑·波拿巴]]被怀疑死于砷中毒，因为在流放地[[圣赫勒拿|圣赫勒拿群岛]]居所墙壁的涂料上就有[[挥发性|挥发性]][[砷化合物|砷化合物]]。

